text: Dražen Silić (; born 25 May 1985) is a Croatian bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Croatia Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
